      restrict-singleton-filterᵐ-false : ∀ m → ¬ P k → filterᵐ P′ m ∣ ❴ k ❵ ᶜ ≡ᵐ filterᵐ P′ m
      restrict-singleton-filterᵐ-false {k} m ¬p = ≡ᵉ.sym (begin
